# 🧠 Khaoula Ziani — Personal Portfolio

Welcome to my personal portfolio website, created using **Hugo + HugoBlox Builder** and hosted on **GitHub Pages**.  
This site highlights my learning journey, skills, and projects as a **cybersecurity student** passionate about technology and digital safety.

